claim.claim-text:
A display comprising:
a relief structure-forming layer having a plurality of relief structure-forming areas and provided on one principal surface of a light transmissive base;
a light reflection layer covering at least a part of the relief structure-forming layer; and
a light scattering layer provided on a side of the light reflection layer of the relief structure-forming layer, being imparted with light transmission performance, while being imparted with light scattering performance in at least a part thereof, characterized in that:
the plurality of relief structure-forming areas have a plurality of convexities or a plurality of concavities having a first surface substantially parallel to the principal surface and a second surface substantially parallel to the first surface;
the light reflection layer is formed in conformity with a shape of the plurality of convexities or concavities;
in each of the plurality of relief structure-forming areas, a vertical interval between the first surface and the second surface is substantially constant;
the plurality of relief structure-forming areas differ from each other by at least either one of the vertical interval between the first surface and the second surface and a height of a virtual plane configured by the first surface; and
the plurality of relief structure-forming areas are arranged in accord with a color image to be displayed.
